notes.body: References: 1. Xiaomei Zhu, Lan Yin, Leroy Hood, David Galas and Ping Ao, Efficiency, Robustness and Stochasticity of Gene Regulatory networks in Systems biology: Lambda switch as a working example, 2006. 2. Adam Arkin, John Ross and Harley H. McAdams, Stochastic kinetic analysis of developmental pathway bifurcation in phage lambda-infected Escherichia coli cells, 1998, Genetics, 149: 1633-1648. 3. GenBank sequence: NC_001416 is the whole genome sequence of phage lambda.
